{"tid":1364311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727 728 全世界要standby","createTime":"2019-07-25T10:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T12:05:03.000Z","uid":252591,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"48ab413d5b5823e39caaa3259a09bf284b90721c","tid":1364311,"uid":252591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"727 728 全世界要standby<br />\n<br />\n之前巴打叫我留tg 請加呢個<br />\n請聽我一言 心戰室<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/thzforlisten2me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fthzforlisten2me&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6T2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=8137a9ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/thzforlisten2me</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係舊 po<br />\n請聽我一言 要嬴呢場運動，一定要智破警渣 (綜合加強版)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322524\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322524</a><br />\n<br />\n鑑於警渣已經發出反對通知書<br />\n擺出一副反對左你仲要黎你死你事既姿態<br />\n有強烈理由相信721 事件會重演<br />\n無警渣 999 cut 線 警署落閘 西鐵飛車/停駛事<br />\n老黑血洗元朗既事情再次出現<br />\n<br />\n沙盤推演<br />\n警渣唔會出現係市中心 最盡只會守哂係村口(埋伏) 同時黑鄉警會以「保鄉違族」既原因主動出手<br />\n<br />\n首先呼籲 727出到元朗既一定要出! <br />\n人數就是關鍵 齊上齊落 唔好落單<br />\n<br />\nFull gear 防具 哨子 長遮<br />\n水 乾糧 電話多部 <br />\n<br />\n出發前要搵定伴 所有人要做到齊上齊落 元朗同朗屏西鐵站都有多個出口 係有被埋伏既絕對可能!<br />\n<br />\n有車既朋友<br />\n要 standby 突發事件義載<br />\n<br />\n消防 救護 孔武有力之士<br />\n要 standby 以防官鄉黑主動出擊<br />\n<br />\n同住屯天元既人保持聯絡<br />\n確保最新資訊流通<br />\n<br />\n外置充電 電筒 充電線 急救用品<br />\n無論出唔出 都要準備定應該突發情況!"},{"pid":"5e383ad7e26c33a645dbe20c81b71cb5ceca72d8","tid":1364311,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:35:07.000Z","msg":"有反對通知書會點"},{"pid":"957fb332c544e2b391db26e0a603d34b3007e155","tid":1364311,"uid":252591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad2fa3537b7e28eef4582ea45dcb5fb4ade2f12","tid":1364311,"uid":181549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:21:22.000Z","msg":"#撤回逃犯條例<br />\n#撤回暴動定性<br />\n#撤銷所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n#追究警隊濫暴<br />\n#立即實行雙普選<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我無野講 我要見律師 我要去醫院<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 獨立建國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n726 機場（和理優）/ QEH 中大百萬大道 （和理 靜坐）<br />\n727 元朗 （和理哭 悼李鵬 祈天父原諒64罪行）<br />\n728 上環 （和理優 追究亂開槍責任）<br />\n84 將軍澳+港島西 （和理優）"},{"pid":"a0de952c8ce2c82e9a816779911ca9bc40b82760","tid":1364311,"uid":252591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ad2fa3537b7e28eef4582ea45dcb5fb4ade2f12","tid":1364311,"uid":181549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:21:22.000Z","msg":"#撤回逃犯條例<br />\n#撤回暴動定性<br />\n#撤銷所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n#追究警隊濫暴<br />\n#立即實行雙普選<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我無野講 我要見律師 我要去醫院<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 獨立建國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n726 機場（和理優）/ QEH 中大百萬大道 （和理 靜坐）<br />\n727 元朗 （和理哭 悼李鵬 祈天父原諒64罪行）<br />\n728 上環 （和理優 追究亂開槍責任）<br />\n84 將軍澳+港島西 （和理優）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00434d14fc070114247600824d085df774859476","tid":1364311,"uid":252591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4603af2af64592cbefaa71621a3ecd829356d8","tid":1364311,"uid":252591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced07bb090504f212a8cfa7b9e5ea72258519a6e","tid":1364311,"uid":252591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:40:16.